CUSTOMIZABLE LEGAL AND MEDICAL CASE MANAGEMENT SOFTWARE

MINDSET’s CaseReview® is a unique software platform specifically designed for attorneys, legal teams, and experts to manage multiple facets of case files including complex medical record review, interactive case indexing, and compiling supporting case data.

Our platform is revolutionizing how legal teams manage and review legal cases, providing an intuitive and low-cost file indexing service designed to save you money. 

IMPROVE Efficiency and Collaboration

Streamline your file review process for every case, enabling your entire legal team—from paralegals to experts—to focus on their responsibilities. By simplifying access to essential details, we help you achieve more successful case outcomes.

Collaborative Case Management with Instant Access to Key Evidence

CaseReview allows multiple people to collaborate on files simultaneously with key event summaries and hyperlinks to source documents for easy access within each file.

Streamlined Access to Case Files and Summaries

Experts can be given access to both the files and the summarized events. This saves the legal team time and money while reviewing the files.

Time Tracking for Accurate Billing

CaseReview tracks the amount of time that an individual has spent reviewing each file, ensuring a correct calculation of billable hours.

The Future of Legal Case Management

Prior to CaseReview, legal software services were designed to address two distinct needs: eDiscovery (electronic compilation and search of relevant records) and cloud-based case management (tracking casework, billing and calendars). Neither of these have built-in systems for organizing and utilizing the vast amounts of stored records throughout the lifecycle of a case.
